==English==
[[Image:Cithare.jpg|thumb|right|200px|A zither]]
===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˈzɪ.ðɝ/
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪðə(r)|-ɪðə(r)]]

===Etymology===
from Latin ''cithara'' > Greek ''κιθάρα'' (lit., guitar)

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[musical instrument]] consisting of a flat [[sounding box]] with numerous [[string]]s, placed on a horizontal surface, and played with a [[plectrum]] and fingertips; similar to a [[dulcimer]].

